<section id="embodiment">
<div class="section-label">Physicality &amp; Motion</div>
<h2><strong>Embodiment</strong> &amp; Gesture</h2>
<p>The body as instrument. These three paradigms explore how physical movement — its speed, direction, rhythm — becomes material for artistic expression.</p>
<div class="embodiment-tabs">
